sequenceDiagram
    actor Owner as Data Owner
    participant FE as Frontend
    participant API as Backend
    participant Celery as Celery Worker
    participant Vast as Vast.ai GPU
    participant FS as File Storage
    participant Qdrant as Qdrant

    Owner->>FE: Open Training Dashboard
    FE->>API: GET /api/v1/training/status
    API-->>FE: { model_version, last_trained, f1_score, pending_changes }

    Owner->>FE: Click "Retrain"
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/training/trigger { type: reindex }
    API->>PG: Create training_job (status: pending)

    Note over API: Pre-flight check:
    Note over API: N new strains, M archived,
    Note over API: P feedback accepted

    API-->>FE: { job_id, estimated_duration }

    API->>Celery: Dispatch re-index task

    loop Per Active Segment
        Celery->>Feat: Extract features (all extractors)
        Feat-->>Celery: Named vectors
        Celery->>Qdrant: Upsert point (named vectors + payload)
        Celery->>PG: Update qdrant_index_state
    end

    loop Per Archived Segment
        Celery->>Qdrant: Delete point
        Celery->>PG: Update qdrant_index_state (is_active=FALSE)
    end

    loop Per Segment (progress updates)
        Celery->>PG: Update training_jobs.progress
        FE->>API: Poll GET /api/v1/training/jobs/{id}
        API-->>FE: { progress: { stage, current, total } }
        FE->>Owner: Show progress bar
    end

    Celery->>PG: Update training_jobs (status: completed)

    Note over Owner: Optional: fine-tune model
    Owner->>FE: Click "Fine-tune Model"
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/training/trigger { type: finetune }
    API->>Celery: Dispatch fine-tune task
    Celery->>Vast: Spin up GPU instance
    Vast->>FS: Download training dataset
    Vast->>Vast: Train EfficientNetB1
    Vast->>FS: Save model weights (.pth)
    Vast->>Celery: Signal completion

    Owner->>FE: Review F1 score (0.92 vs 0.89)
    Owner->>FE: Click "Deploy Model"
    FE->>API: POST /api/v1/training/jobs/{id}/deploy
    API->>Celery: Re-index all with new model
    Celery->>Qdrant: Upsert with new features
    API->>PG: Update model_version, is_deployed=TRUE
